This course treats use of modern digital solutions in working with learners with special educational needs.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The main goal of the course is to enhance students' capability to apply educational technology safely and efficiently in special education in teaching students with special educational needs, including in developing their digital literacy.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  By the end of the course the student: 1)	is able to apply effectively modern technological solutions in formation developmental and learning environment for learners with special educational needs; 2)	is able to use educational technologies for monitoring and evaluating development of students with special educational needs; 3)	understands the risks accompanied with spread of digital culture and is able to cope with these in guiding children and in counselling parents.
